# Stage 4: The Echo's Effects

label stage4_echo_effects:
    scene bg garden with fade

    "Echo" "The withering. The whispers. The temporal anomalies."
    "Echo" "These are not my intent. They are my nature."
    "Echo" "I exist at the intersection of dimensions."
    "Echo" "Where I touch your reality, reality... changes."

    $ clues_found.append("echo_nature")
    $ evidence_score += 15

    show y at left with dissolve

    y "So the disturbances aren't attacks. They're side effects."

    "Echo" "Yes. I am poison to your world. Not through malice."
    "Echo" "But through incompatibility."

    jump stage4_analyze_clues
